### Umgebungsvariablen
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json

###
### CUSTOMER API TESTS
###

### Alle Kunden abrufen
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Einen spezifischen Kunden abrufen
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers/1
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Alle Bestellungen eines Kunden abrufen
GET {{baseUrl}}/customers/1/orders
Accept: {{contentType}}

### Neuen Kunden erstellen
POST {{baseUrl}}/customers
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Max Mustermann",
  "email": "max.mustermann@example.com",
  "address": "Musterstraße 123, 1234 Musterstadt",
  "phoneNumber": "+43 123 456789"
}

### Kunden aktualisieren
PUT {{baseUrl}}/customers/1
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Maximilian Mustermann",
  "email": "maximilian.mustermann@example.com",
  "address": "Musterstraße 123, 1234 Musterstadt",
  "phoneNumber": "+43 123 456789"
}

### Kunden löschen
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/customers/3
Accept: {{contentType}}

